snippet.title: Predecessor - Official Release Date Teaser Trailer | Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Predecessor is an online strategy MOBA developed by Omeda Studios. Players must master teamwork and strategy to reign victorious in this Unreal Engine 5 title. Utilize over 30 unique Heroes with distinct play styles and abilities. Take a look at the Gamescom 2024 teaser trailer for the release date of Predecessor, launching on August 20 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam and Epic Games Store).

#Predecessor #Gamescom2024 #Gaming
